# Coding Style

- Prefer functional components and async/await.
- Services in `src/services/` are pure business logic; no React imports.
- DB access only through `src/db/` modules, not directly in components.
- Types live in `src/types/`; avoid duplicating interfaces.
- Use named exports; default export only for Next.js pages.
- Environment variables: `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` for client-safe values only.
